---
// ContactFaqSection.astro - 聯絡我們與常見問答區塊
---

<section id="contact" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12">
      
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-8 relative inline-block">
          聯絡我們
          <span class="absolute bottom-[-10px] left-0 w-12 h-1 bg-primary rounded-full"></span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div>
              <p class="text-primary font-bold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Organizer</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">次世代超高速傳輸系統<br/>整合教學聯盟中心</h3>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 group">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm shrink-0 group-hover:bg-sky-500 group-hover:shadow-md group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
                  <img src="/images/mail.png" alt="Email" class="w-6 h-6 object-contain filter brightness-0 invert" style="filter: brightness(0) invert(1);" />
                </div>
                <div class="pt-1">
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase mb-0.5">Email</p>
                  <!-- <a href="mailto:mcpc2026@example.edu.tw" class="text-slate-700 font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors break-all">
                    mcpc2026@example.edu.tw
                  </a> -->
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 group">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm shrink-0 group-hover:bg-sky-500 group-hover:shadow-md group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
                  <img src="/images/phone.png" alt="Phone" class="w-6 h-6 object-contain filter brightness-0 invert" style="filter: brightness(0) invert(1);" />
                </div>
                <div class="pt-1">
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase mb-0.5">Phone</p>
                  <p class="text-slate-700 font-medium">(04) 2284-0688 分機 615</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 group">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm shrink-0 group-hover:bg-sky-500 group-hover:shadow-md group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
                  <img src="/images/clock.png" alt="Hours" class="w-6 h-6 object-contain filter brightness-0 invert" style="filter: brightness(0) invert(1);" />
                </div>
                <div class="pt-1">
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase mb-0.5">Service Hours</p>
                  <p class="text-slate-700 font-medium">週一至週五 09:00 - 17:00</p>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-8">常見問答</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-100 open:bg-white open:border-primary transition-colors duration-300">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 cursor-pointer font-bold text-slate-700 hover:text-primary transition-colors list-none">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-primary font-black text-lg">Q.</span>
                請問可以跨校或跨系組隊嗎？
              </span>
              <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 border border-slate-200 group-open:rotate-180 group-open:bg-primary group-open:text-white group-open:border-primary transition-all duration-300">▼</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 pl-12 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              可以。我們非常鼓勵跨領域與跨校交流，只要所有成員皆為在學學生即可。但需明確指定一所學校為主要報名單位。
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-100 open:bg-white open:border-primary transition-colors duration-300">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 cursor-pointer font-bold text-slate-700 hover:text-primary transition-colors list-none">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-primary font-black text-lg">Q.</span>
                一個隊伍可以有多少人？
              </span>
               <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 border border-slate-200 group-open:rotate-180 group-open:bg-primary group-open:text-white group-open:border-primary transition-all duration-300">▼</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 pl-12 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              每隊人數限制為 2 至 5 人，且必須設有一名指導教授（指導教授可同時指導多隊）。
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-100 open:bg-white open:border-primary transition-colors duration-300">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 cursor-pointer font-bold text-slate-700 hover:text-primary transition-colors list-none">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-primary font-black text-lg">Q.</span>
                初賽通過後，可以更換隊員嗎？
              </span>
               <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 border border-slate-200 group-open:rotate-180 group-open:bg-primary group-open:text-white group-open:border-primary transition-all duration-300">▼</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 pl-12 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              原則上不可更換。若有特殊不可抗力因素（如退學、休學），需提出相關證明並經由主辦單位審核同意後方可變更。
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-100 open:bg-white open:border-primary transition-colors duration-300">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 cursor-pointer font-bold text-slate-700 hover:text-primary transition-colors list-none">
               <span class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-primary font-black text-lg">Q.</span>
                決賽一定要有實體作品展示嗎？
              </span>
               <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 border border-slate-200 group-open:rotate-180 group-open:bg-primary group-open:text-white group-open:border-primary transition-all duration-300">▼</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 pl-12 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              視參賽組別而定。若是「技術實作組」建議有實體或原型 Demo；若是「數位應用組」則可以 App 互動展示為主。
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>